+## Suggested pilot
+
+Use a contained, high-value cluster:
+
+- Southern California hotel wage and health-benefit obligations
+- 3–7 properties
+- payroll, benefits, and property operations stakeholders
+- one decision record
+- 3–5 linked controls
+- post-cutover assurance
+
+This pilot exercises the full causal chain without requiring nationwide integration on day one.
diff --git a/product/MIGRATION.md b/product/MIGRATION.md
